{"name": "pysegd3", "metadata": {"name": "pysegd3", "version": "1.1.0", "classifiers": ["Operating System :: Microsoft :: Windows", "Operating System :: POSIX :: Linux", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": "", "license": "GPL3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["numpy", "pytest", "matplotlib", "tempoo"], "summary": "", "upload_time": 1707471767}, "documentation": ["# PYSEGD3 \n\nStandalone package to read/write segd rev3 files in python\n\n## Install \n### From Pypi\n```bash\npip install pysegd3\n``` \n\n### Form Github (sources)\n```bash \ngit clone https://github.com/mlehujeur/pysegd3.git\npython -m pip install -e pysegd3 \n```\n\n## Usages\n### Load a segd rev 3 file\n```python\nfrom pysegd3.readsegd3 import read_segd_rev3\n\nfor (trace_header, trace_data) in read_segd_rev3(segdfilename):\n    print(trace_header)  # a python dictionnary built like obspy trace stats header\n    print(trace_data)  # a numpy array\n```\n\n### Load as an obspy stream\nObspy is not included in this package\n```bash\npip install obspy\n```\n\n```python\nfrom pysegd3.readsegd3_as_obspy import read_segd_rev3_as_obspy\n\nstream = read_segd_rev3_as_obspy(segdfilename)\nprint(stream)\n```\n\n"], "modules": [{"name": "pysegd3-1.1.0.data.scripts.readsegd3_as_obspy", "documentation": ["Copyright (C) 2024  maximilien.lehujeur\nsegd3 -> obspy converter \nNote : obspy is not a dependency of this package, install it manually", "!python"], "functions": [{"name": "pysegd3-1.1.0.data.scripts.readsegd3_as_obspy.read_segd_rev3_as_obspy", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "filename", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "verbose", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "headonly", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "obspy.core.stream.Stream", "xref": {"fqname": "obspy.core.stream.Stream", "project": null}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["read a segd file and pack it into a obspy Stream"]}], "variables": [{"name": "pysegd3-1.1.0.data.scripts.readsegd3_as_obspy.stream", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "pysegd3.readsegd3_as_obspy", "documentation": ["Copyright (C) 2024  maximilien.lehujeur\nsegd3 -> obspy converter \nNote : obspy is not a dependency of this package, install it manually", "!/usr/bin/env python"], "functions": [{"name": "pysegd3.readsegd3_as_obspy.read_segd_rev3_as_obspy", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "filename", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "verbose", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "headonly", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "obspy.core.stream.Stream", "xref": {"fqname": "obspy.core.stream.Stream", "project": null}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["read a segd file and pack it into a obspy Stream"]}], "variables": [{"name": "pysegd3.readsegd3_as_obspy.stream", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "pysegd3-1.1.0.data.scripts.readsegd3", "documentation": ["Copyright (C) 2024  maximilien.lehujeur\nBasic stand alone reader for SEGD rev 3.X", "!python"], "functions": [{"name": "pysegd3-1.1.0.data.scripts.readsegd3.print_nested_dict", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "dct", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "indent", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "pysegd3-1.1.0.data.scripts.readsegd3.segd_timestamp", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "bytes_in", "type": {"n